#: lib/retro_hex_chat/commands/handlers/ns.ex:85
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Register and protect your nickname with a password through NickServ.\n"
"Subcommands: register <password>, identify <password>, ghost <nick> <password>, info [nick], drop <password>, help.\n"
"Register: claims current nickname. Identify: authenticates each session.\n"
"Ghost: disconnects a stale session using the registered nickname's password."
msgstr "Register dan melindungi nama panggilan Anda dengan password melalui NickServ.\n"
"Sub perintah: register <password>, identifikasi <password>, hantu <nick> <password>, info [nama panggilan], turunkan <password>, tolong.\n"
"Register: klaim nama panggilan saat ini. Identifikasi: otentikasi setiap sesi.\n"
"Ghost: memutuskan sesi yang basi menggunakan sandi nama panggilan terdaftar."

